    <div class="main review-item" id="7780616">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7780616/" class="title-link">《黑格尔导论》（1、10章）读书笔记</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7780616"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/46851891/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u46851891-9.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/46851891/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Umsicht</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-02-19"
      class="main-meta">2016-02-19 17:35:45</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7780616_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  调和宗教本体（启示）与逻辑本体（哲学）的工作是西方哲学本体论的主线之一，前者是信仰的对象，后者是认识的对象。两者也被称为是雅典与耶路撒冷的“双城记”。两者分殊明显但都被当作形而上学（metaphysics/φυσικάμετά）的客观实体。人是“主体”而非实体，人...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7780616_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7780616_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8461998">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8461998/" class="title-link">关于sein的翻译问题</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8461998"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/killmeifyouwant/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u49099843-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/killmeifyouwant/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Walt</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2017-04-06"
      class="main-meta">2017-04-06 15:13:45</span>
</div>

  </header>

